---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Glazed - Privacy Policy">
	<div class="pt-32 pb-20 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-6">
                <span class="text-white">Privacy </span>
                <span class="text-brand-primary text-glow">Policy</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-mono">Last updated: February 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none bg-brand-surface border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-8 md:p-12 space-y-8">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">1. No Telemetry</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Glazed Client does <strong class="text-white">not</strong> collect, store, or transmit any personal data, usage statistics, analytics, or telemetry to us or any third party. The Software is fully open-source — you can verify this yourself by inspecting the code.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">2. Local Storage</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">The Software stores configuration files and module settings locally on your device within your <code class="bg-black/50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded text-gray-300 text-sm">.minecraft</code> folder. These files exist solely for the Software's functionality and never leave your machine.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">3. Discord Webhooks</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Some modules (such as Coord Snapper, Rain Noti, Llama ESP, Pillager ESP, and Advanced Stash Finder) support optional Discord webhook integration. If you choose to configure a webhook URL, the module will send data to that webhook.</p>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-2">This is entirely <strong class="text-white">opt-in</strong> and <strong class="text-white">user-configured</strong>. We do not provide, control, or receive data from any webhooks. The data goes directly from your game client to the Discord webhook URL you set up.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">4. Third-Party Dependencies</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Glazed requires third-party software to function:</p>
                <ul class="text-gray-400 mt-2 space-y-1 list-disc list-inside">
                    <li><strong class="text-white">Meteor Client</strong> — base client framework</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-white">Fabric Loader & API</strong> — mod loading platform</li>
                    <li><strong class="text-white">Baritone</strong> — pathfinding (optional)</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mt-3">We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third-party projects. Review their respective privacy policies for details on how they handle data.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">5. This Website</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">This website is a static site hosted on GitHub Pages. We do not use cookies, trackers, or analytics services. GitHub may collect standard server logs as part of their hosting — see <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement" target="_blank" class="text-brand-primary hover:text-brand-accent transition-colors">GitHub's Privacy Statement</a> for details.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">6. Changes</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Any changes to this policy will be posted on this page with an updated date. Since the Software has no auto-update mechanism that contacts our servers, check back here periodically.</p>
            </div>

            <div>
                <h3 class="text-white text-lg font-bold mb-3">7. Contact</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">Questions about this Privacy Policy? Reach out via our Discord community.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
